      "text": "（今日は星見市で野外フェスが開催される日だ）\n（サニーピースもステージでパフォーマンスを披露した）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(There’s an outdoor festival at Hoshimi City today.)\n(Sunny Peace will be performing on-stage)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.8539653102556866,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
