      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 7.963197040557864
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫か、怜\nいつもより、息が上がっているみたいだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you ok‚ Rei?\nYou seem more out of breath than usual.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.864447714732243,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……はぁ……大丈夫です……\nちょっと気合が入り過ぎただけですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*huff* *huff* I’m fine…\nI got a little too worked up‚ that’s all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.470827529206872,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 19.468616533279455
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それなんだが……今日の怜のダンス\nいつもと比べてぎこちない気がしたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "About that… To my eyes‚\nyour dancing seemed less fluid than usual today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.133333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 25.76861653327946
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "……っ\n私は、いつも通り踊ったつもりです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…!\nI thought was just doing what I usually do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "具体的に、どこがぎこちなく感じたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Were there any specific things that made you feel that way?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.49625835418703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 32.97757349014287
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "普段より、動きも表情も硬かったと思う\n気のせいか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your movements and expression looked more rigid than usual.\nI could’ve just imagined it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.4138659000397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "…………そう、ですか\nやっぱり……そう見えちゃってたんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I see.\nSo… it looked that way to you as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.15929670333865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 44.65929670333865
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
