      "text": "いや、そこまでは言ってない\nいつも通り高いレベルでまとまってはいたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It wasn’t that bad.\nIt was just a little short of your normal high standards.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.03904445872588,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
