      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…\nYou make some astute observations… from time to time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 290.99375057855883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-rei032.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、そうですね\n先生に習ってきたことを、最大限活かせばいい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you’re right.\nThe best way for me to repay my coach",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 300.4604172452253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
