      "startTime": 308.227083911892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-koh020.m4a",
      "text": "……そうだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 312.49375057855866,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-rei034.m4a",
      "text": "はい。もう後ろめたく思うのはやめます\n今すぐには無理かもしれないですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll stop wallowing in guilt‚\neven if I can’t change overnight…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 317.55644968152046,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_03-rei035.m4a",
      "text": "じゃないと、今日みたいに\n見に来てくれた先生にも、失礼ですから",
      "translations": {
